snippet.title: Amber Heard Bombarded With Questions Of Settlement With Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Thursday, June 16, 2016: Amber Heard was spotted visiting an office building in West Hollywood and was peppered with questions about her ongoing legal dealing with ex-Johnny Depp's legal team.  X17online.com
